    <h2>3.</h2>
    (20) What is a parameter?
    <div id="myCollapsibleExample"><a href="#demo4" data-toggle="collapse">Answer</a></div>
    <div id="demo4" class="collapse"> A parameter is the information a 
        function needs to perform its job, e.g., how long should the phone vibrate, or how
        big a circle should be drawn.
    </div>
